3/biomet/asaa052&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt;, for a proof for mean bias reduction in logistic regression). 'brglm2' also provides pre-fit and post-fit methods for detecting separation and infinite maximum likelihood estimates in binomial response generalized linear models." />
